<subSubSection id="BCDD2DE8F5BA8A047A284D632F8DCE13" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" type="notes">
<paragraph id="15349FBD5CC7761E73DAA0E21B9484D9" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997">Notes</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C1D00B8AA6DD7552AC46C86D021D2E35" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997">
Reported from Greece by 
<bibRefCitation id="E98D9410E2D56D3F63264A10797C5E4A" author="Xenopoulou, D" journalOrPublisher="University of Athens, Athens" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" title="Study of the distribution and temporal variations of the soft substrate benthic fauna of the island of Skiathos. MSc thesis" year="1987">Xenopoulou (1987)</bibRefCitation>
, also found by 
<bibRefCitation id="09D5F81AC14838E7F48D35F1EB268E63" author="Papageorgiou, Nafsika" journalOrPublisher="Estuarine, Coastal and Shelf Science" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination="643 - 653" title="Multicausal environmental severity: A flexible framework for microtidal sandy beaches and the role of polychaetes as an indicator taxon" volume="70" year="2006">Papageorgiou et al. (2006)</bibRefCitation>
(unpublished data). In the Mediterranean also reported from the Gulf of Lions (
<bibRefCitation id="EC4CC337CDB769AAF05416DF013F816D" author="Laubier, Lucien" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin du Museum d'Histoire Naturelle, Paris" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination="1097 - 1148" title="Paraonidae (Polychetes sedentaires) de Mediterranee" volume="113" year="1974">Laubier and Ramos 1974</bibRefCitation>
), Spain (
<bibRefCitation id="8F405F6973BE84782AE16E60CEB9F721" author="Torres-Gavila, Francisco Javier" journalOrPublisher="Universitat de Valencia, Valencia" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" title="Estudio faunistico, ecologico y ambiental de la fauna de anelidos poliquetos de sustratos sueltos de las Islas Chafarinas (Mar de Alboran, S. W. Mediterraneo)" year="2008">Torres-Gavila 2008</bibRefCitation>
), Italy (
<bibRefCitation id="5DFB2CC1FD5C3037C43681267F05C2E6" author="Castelli, A" journalOrPublisher="Biologia Marina Mediterranea" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination="323 - 373" title="AnnelidaPolychaeta" volume="15" year="2008">Castelli et al. 2008</bibRefCitation>
) and the Adriatic (
<bibRefCitation id="55E203FAF7560A62626579029A629B66" author="Mikac, Barbara" journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination="1 - 17" title="A sea of worms: polychaete checklist of the Adriatic Sea" volume="3943" year="2015">Mikac 2015</bibRefCitation>
), otherwise distributed along the Atlantic coasts of Europe and North America.
</paragraph>
